data.description: Charming home in an established neighborhood in the heart of Edinburg.  This spacious 2850 sq ft residence boasts 4 beds, 3 baths, and features a family room, dining room, and 2 bonus rooms. Whether you desire a home office, a playroom, a gym, or a hobby space, these versatile and spacious bonus rooms can be tailored to suit your needs. Adorned with stylish shiplap accents, the house exudes character and charm. Recently updated with a NEW A/C unit. Step outside into the backyard oasis, where you'll discover beautiful landscaping that surrounds a sparkling pool. Spend your summer days lounging by the poolside, hosting barbecues, or simply enjoying the tranquility of your private outdoor retreat. This gem is situated on a large lot and offers both comfort and convenience with nearby amenities, schools, and parks just moments away. Don't miss the opportunity to call this beautiful property your home.
